# Task 3 - Validation & Error Handling

## Overview

This project was developed as part of the ApexPlanet Web Development Internship. The objective of this task was to improve the application by implementing client-side validation, server-side validation, and error handling mechanisms.

## Features Implemented

### Client-Side Validation

* Name validation
* Password length validation
* Phone number validation
* JavaScript alert messages

### Server-Side Validation

* Email format validation
* Password validation
* Phone number validation
* Duplicate email checking

### Error Handling

* User-friendly error messages
* Invalid input detection
* Registration failure handling

### Security Improvements

* Password hashing
* Prepared statements
* Input validation

### User Experience Enhancements

* Success messages
* Error alerts
* Delete confirmation popup

## Technologies Used

* PHP
* JavaScript
* MySQL
* Bootstrap 5
* HTML5
* CSS3

## Files Modified

* register.php
* manage_users.php

## Validation Rules

* Name must contain at least 3 characters
* Password must contain at least 6 characters
* Phone number must contain 10 digits
* Email must be valid
* Duplicate email addresses are not allowed

## Learning Outcomes

* Client-side form validation
* Server-side data validation
* Error handling techniques
* Improved application security
* Better user experience

